Privacy of Information. You acknowledge that SCE will receive certain personal, private and/or confidential information in connection with your use of My Account; and that absent your express authorization, SCE will not rent, sell or otherwise make available to any third party for any reason any of this information that personally identifies you or your SCE account, other than to provide My Account services or to comply with applicable laws or regulations, including CPUC or court orders.
	 
