A Smart Thermostat Is the Smartest Way to Get a $125 Sign-Up Bonus See Options

        With up to a $125 sign-up bonus, it's never been a better time to enroll your new or existing smart thermostat through our qualified service providers who represent brands such as Alarm.com, ecobee, Honeywell, Lux, Nest, Radio Thermostat Company of America, Sensi™ Wi-Fi Programmable Thermostat, Venstar, and Zen Thermostat™.





Want to Take Advantage of This Special Offer, Save Energy, and Help the Environment?
Successfully enroll your smart thermostat in our Save Power Days Program through one of our approved service providers
    and receive $125 in rebates from SCE and SoCalGas®.† Plus, your participation in a program can earn you up to $60
    in bill credits every year.‡





How to Get Your $125 Sign-Up Bonus

 Purchase a new smart thermostat or enroll your existing one (see product and program options below).§
Receive a $125 credit on your SCE bill. Program funded by SCE and SoCalGas.
The $125 sign-up bonus is for joint SCE and SoCalGas customers. If you are an SCE customer, but not a customer of SoCalGas, you'll receive a $75 sign-up bonus from SCE only.

Continue to Earn Up to $60 Annually in Bill Credits 
Additionally, you'll receive bill credits when program events are called and your electricity usage is lowered using your smart thermostat. 








The Benefits of a Smart Thermostat

Hassle-Free Home TemperaturesSmart thermostats learn your schedule and home temperature preferences so they can lower and raise your home's air-conditioning temperature while you come and go.

Easy to UseAdjust the temperature from anywhere with a mobile app or your tablet and computer.
Saves EnergyAlong with learning when you are home and away, a smart thermostat can use local weather information to help control your energy costs.




