Got questions? Check out our Billing & Payments FAQ  >

 
Level Pay Plan
As a residential customer, or a commercial GS-1 customer, you may qualify to enroll in our Level Pay Plan. The plan evens your monthly payments to avoid big spikes on your energy statements, even when your energy usage changes from one season to another, allowing your payments to be predictable.
View our Level Pay Plan FAQs for more information
Call to enroll: 1-800-434-2365






 


